Trade/Device Name(s): Stat Profile Prime Plus Analyzer System
Regulation Name(s): Blood gases (PCO2, PO2) and blood pH test system
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Stat Profile Prime Plus Analyzer System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Stat Profile Prime Plus Analyzer System for quantitative determination of pH, pCO2, and pO2 in heparinized whole blood.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for use by healthcare professionals in clinical laboratory settings and point-of-care for quantitative determination of pH, pCO2, and pO2 in heparinized arterial and venous whole blood to aid in the diagnosis and treatment of acid-base disturbances.
